belongs_to_collection.name: The Mistress of the World Collection

original_title: Die Herrin der Welt 6. Teil - Die Frau mit den Millionarden
overview: Thanks to the treasure of the Queen of Sheba, Maud, who now calls herself Fergusson, has become an immensely wealthy woman. The plane that rescued her and Allan Stanley from Ophir belongs to newspaper king Fletcher, who reports on the rescue operation on the front pages of his newspapers.
title: The mistress of the world, Part VI: The woman with the millionaires
